OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777551071
OL,3,CMan who killed father-of-two in
OL,4,CAustralia found mentally unfit for
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA man who killed a father-of-two from
OL,8,FCounty Durham in an Australian town
OL,9,Fhas been declared mentally unfit to
OL,10,Fstand trial.
OL,12,FCourt documents say 30-year-old Royce
OL,13,FMallett was visiting the town of
OL,14,FAlbury, in New South Wales, in July
OL,15,F2024, when he was stabbed once in the
OL,16,Fchest while sitting in the driver's
OL,17,Fseat of a car parked outside the Hume
OL,18,FInn Motel.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
