PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777551071
OL,3,CMan who killed father-of-two in
OL,4,CAustralia found mentally unfit for
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHis attacker, David Summers-Smith, has
OL,8,Fschizophrenia and was displaying
OL,9,Fsymptoms of psychosis at the time of
OL,10,Fthe incident.
OL,12,FHe pleaded not guilty to the murder
OL,13,Fdue to mental impairment.
OL,15,FSupreme Court justice Dina Yehia on
OL,16,FTuesday (28 April) determined Summers-
OL,17,FSmith did commit the murder but could
OL,18,Fnot be held criminally responsible.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
