OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777551071
OL,3,CMan who killed father-of-two in
OL,4,CAustralia found mentally unfit for
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FIn her consideration, Justice Yehia
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am satisfied that the accused
OL,9,Fhas established on a balance of
OL,10,Fprobabilities that at the time he
OL,11,Fstabbed the deceased, he was suffering
OL,12,Ffrom a mental health impairment that
OL,13,Fhad the effect that he did not know
OL,14,Fthat the act was wrong: that is, he
OL,15,Fcould not reason with a moderate
OL,16,Fdegree of sense and composure about
OL,17,Fwhether the act, as perceived by
OL,18,Freasonable people, was wrong."
OL,26,@pD@GOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
