PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777551071
OL,3,CMan who killed father-of-two in
OL,4,CAustralia found mentally unfit for
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FMr Mallett had two children who were
OL,8,Fboth under the age of five at the time
OL,9,Fof his death.
OL,11,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,12,Fby Justice Yehia, Mr Mallett's partner
OL,13,FCaitlin O'Keeffe said his death has
OL,14,Fcaused immense emotional and financial
OL,15,Fstrain for the family.
OL,17,F"It affects not just today but every
OL,18,Ffuture moment that he should have been
OL,19,Fpart of, and everyday moments that
OL,20,Fhe's already missed," Ms O'Keefe said
OL,21,Fin a letter.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777551071
OL,3,CMan who killed father-of-two in
OL,4,CAustralia found mentally unfit for
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe court also heard Mr Mallett's
OL,8,Ffather Roy, of Haswell, near Durham,
OL,9,Fno longer enjoys the hobbies he used
OL,10,Fto share with his son and struggles to
OL,11,Ffind the motivation to do anything.
OL,13,FMr Mallett's mother Felicity told ITV
OL,14,FNews Tyne Tees earlier this month that
OL,15,Fattending the Australian court in
OL,16,Fperson was something she had to do.
OL,18,FAny potential recovery for Summers-
OL,19,FSmith will be monitored by the Mental
OL,20,FHealth Review tribunal, which has the
OL,21,Fpower to revise his detention order.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
